I changed it to this which instead `assert`s that `aMessage` is long enough to contain the metadata before reading it.
```
void CoapBase::CoapMetadata::ReadFrom(const Message &aMessage)
{
    uint16_t length = aMessage.GetLength();

    assert(length >= sizeof(*this));
    aMessage.Read(length - sizeof(*this), sizeof(*this), this);
}
```

