I'm going to add this to the documentation, they are mainly for renaming config keys. In our case, we currently have `cursorBlinkRate` and `codeMirror.cursorBlinkRate` from the CodeMirror options patches. So the following code will make all `cursorBlinkRate` into `codeMirror.cursorBlinkRate`, unless `codeMirror.cursorBlinkRate` is already defined, then delete the `cursorBlinkRate` key.

```ts
createDeprecatedConfigOption({
  key: "cursorBlinkRate",
  changeTo: (value: number) => ({
    "codeMirror.cursorBlinkRate": value,
  }),
});
```

